trans-unit.source: Trains an anomaly detection model on a training set
trans-unit.target: Trains an anomaly detection model on a training set

trans-unit.source: The <ui>Train Anomaly Detection Model</ui> module takes an untrained anomaly detection model, such as that produced by the <link xlink:href="62839cbe-2ae3-4b64-ada4-ad6eba89444a" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">One-Class SVM Model</link> modules, and an unlabeled dataset.
trans-unit.target: The <ui>Train Anomaly Detection Model</ui> module takes an untrained anomaly detection model, such as that produced by the <link xlink:href="62839cbe-2ae3-4b64-ada4-ad6eba89444a" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">One-Class SVM Model</link> modules, and an unlabeled dataset.

trans-unit.source: It returns a trained anomaly detection model, as well as a set of labels for the training data.
trans-unit.target: It returns a trained anomaly detection model, as well as a set of labels for the training data.
